<i>noun</i>: 휴양 [휴양], 위락 [위락], 레크리에이션 [] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>휴양 [휴양]</dt><br>
<dd>rest; recreation; recuperation</dd><br>
<dd>편안히 쉬면서 건강을 잘 돌봄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of taking care of one's health by relaxing.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>위락 [위락]</dt><br>
<dd>recreation; amusement</dd><br>
<dd>시설 등을 이용하여 편안하게 쉬면서 피로를 풀고 즐김.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of having a good time while relaxing, relieving fatigue by using a facility, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>레크리에이션 []</dt><br>
<dd>recreation</dd><br>
<dd>몸과 마음의 피로를 풀고 새로운 힘을 얻기 위해 즐기는 놀이나 운동.</dd><br>
<dd>A game or exercise enjoyed in order to relieve the exhaustion of the body and mind and gain new energy.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>